TopicTitle: KSP Stuck On Loading Screen Forever

Articles.Content:
There is a problem with KSP (modded with Linbol System Rebirth) where KSP is stuck on the loading screen (into the home screen) forever. This bug was not present the last time I opened KSP.

https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/s99qy2h50m4ff3db9kt7l/KSP.log?rlkey=e1qpweuhtvw1vdclyqy9q0pdy&dl=0

Clear your mod's files and run it again without it, see if that works. Is only your mod and kopernicus installed?

Edited July 29, 2023 by Watermel00n

Looks like some engine mod is missing B9 Part Switch, but that's incidental
